com.centurylink.mdw.hub.servlet

Class SoapServlet

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
        • com.centurylink.mdw.hub.servlet.ServiceServlet
          • com.centurylink.mdw.hub.servlet.SoapServlet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    @WebServlet(urlPatterns="/SOAP/*",
            loadOnStartup=1)
public class SoapServlet
extends ServiceServlet
    General SOAP listener servlet corresponding to mdw.wsdl. Request content is pulled out of the SOAP envelope and forwarded to the MDW external event handler mechanism.
